column2: SELECT      p.ra, p.dec,             pz.z as phz ,pz.zErr as phzErr,      s.z,            z.spiral, z.elliptical,         p.petroMag_u,    p.petroMag_g,    p.petroMag_r,    p.petroMag_i,    p.petroMag_z,   p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z,      p.modelMag_u,    p.modelMag_g,    p.modelMag_r,    p.modelMag_i,    p.modelMag_z,   p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z,      p.extinction_u,  p.extinction_g,  p.extinction_r,  p.extinction_i,  p.extinction_z,       ((p.petroMag_u-p.extinction_u)-(p.petroMag_r-p.extinction_r)) as u_minus_r,    ((p.petroMag_r-p.extinction_r)-(p.petroMag_z-p.extinction_z)) as r_minus_z into mydb.PhotoETGcat from PhotoObjAll AS p           LEFT JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID = p.objID     LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON sp.objID = p.objID   LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = sp.specobjid   LEFT JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = sp.specobjid   WHERE      p.type          = #   AND p.petroMagErr_u > #   AND p.petroMagErr_g > #   AND p.petroMagErr_r > #   AND p.petroMagErr_i > #   AND p.petroMagErr_z > #      AND pz.zErr         > #   AND pz.photoErrorClass > #    AND pz.z < #      AND ((p.petroMagErr_u-p.extinction_u)-(p.petroMagErr_r-p.extinction_r))>#   AND ((p.petroMagErr_r-p.extinction_r)-(p.petroMagErr_z-p.extinction_z))<#   AND ((p.petroMagErr_r-p.extinction_r)-(p.petroMagErr_z-p.extinction_z))>#   AND ((p.petroMagErr_u-p.extinction_u)-(p.petroMagErr_r-p.extinction_r))>#+#*((p.petroMagErr_r-p.extinction_r)-(p.petroMagErr_z-p.extinction_z))
